This privacy policy pertains to the Findroid CE app.

Findroid CE does not collect or access any personal information. No identifying information or user data of any kind is made available to third-parties.

This Privacy Policy is effective as of March 28th, 2026 and will remain in effect except with respect to any changes in its provisions in the future, which will be in effect immediately after being posted on this page.

Findroid CE is a community fork of Findroid, published by midasvo. Inquiries can be submitted via https://github.com/midasvo/findroid-ce/issues.
